    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next owner. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it runs like a dream! I\u2019m looking to get this to a new home soon, so I\u2019ve set a really fair price to get things moving. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love to chat!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
