    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I'm selling my trusty car, and let me tell you, it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my trips around town. It runs great, looks lovely, and is totally ready for its next big adventure with a new owner. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 32500.0,
