    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, managed by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains composed with a factory-spec M-variable differential providing optimal mechanical grip. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings for tactile steering feedback and turn-in precision. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior maintains a deep luster, while the Nappa leather interior shows honest wear consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle. Mechanically robust and ready for spirited canyon carving.",
